@startuml class_modes_scientific
title Operation Set Hierarchy — Scientific Mode (PR #353)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam backgroundColor white

abstract class BaseOperationSet {
  # _record_callback : Optional[Callable]
  # _record(result)
  + {abstract} get_operations() : dict[str, Callable]
}

class BasicOperations {
  + get_operations() : dict
}

class AdvancedOperations {
  + get_operations() : dict
}

class ScientificOperations << NEW >> {
  + __init__(record_callback: Optional[Callable])
  + get_operations() : dict
  + sin(x)   + cos(x)   + tan(x)
  + asin(x)  + acos(x)  + atan(x)
  + sinh(x)  + cosh(x)  + tanh(x)
  + exp(x)   + ln(x)
  + degrees(x) + radians(x)
}

note right of ScientificOperations
  13 trig/hyperbolic/exponential ops.
  Each method calls _record(result)
  before returning.
  SCIENTIFIC_OPERATIONS frozenset
  defined in src/modes/operations.py
end note

BaseOperationSet <|-- BasicOperations
BaseOperationSet <|-- AdvancedOperations
BaseOperationSet <|-- ScientificOperations

@enduml
